== 爭議 ==
阮民安的個人操守備受爭議。其舊愛曾控訴他欠下財務公司巨債而不還款，並在同居期間多次盜取對方財物<ref>{{Cite web|title=【黃絲男神搞到前度一身債】舊愛向阮民安對質被拒：佢一蚊都冇還｜壹週刊|url=https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_715446_0|accessdate=|author=|date=|last=|format=|work=壹週刊|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200102003604/https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_715446_0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但其指對方惡意中傷他，並表示已將事年交給律師處理<ref>{{Cite web|title=被舊愛爆八達通都偷 阮民安Tommy指對方抹黑：交晒畀律師處理|url=https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/414132/被舊愛爆八達通都偷-阮民安tommy指對方抹黑-交晒畀律師處理|accessdate=|author=|date=2019-12-25|last=董欣琪|format=|work=香港01|publisher=|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707171958/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/414132/%E8%A2%AB%E8%88%8A%E6%84%9B%E7%88%86%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E9%83%BD%E5%81%B7-%E9%98%AE%E6%B0%91%E5%AE%89tommy%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91-%E4%BA%A4%E6%99%92%E7%95%80%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%99%95%E7%90%86|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2019年曾因演唱會未能舉行後遲遲未肯退款給已買票之人士，被報章指「食人血饅頭」<ref>{{Cite web|title=【申請3月紅館】阮民安集資開騷承諾退票 一拖再拖被指食人血饅頭|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20191201/ZU6DPD7GDWCEPMFKN2LLBGFPIU/|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|work=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|publisher=|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708022142/https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20191201/ZU6DPD7GDWCEPMFKN2LLBGFPIU/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時亦有報導指其曾多次嘗試申請不同場地表演，但懷疑遭政治打壓而被場地方拒絕其申請<ref>{{Cite web|title=疑遭政治打壓 阮民安申請伊館麥花臣場館開騷被拒 (18:42) - 20191024 - SHOWBIZ|url=https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191024/1571910966096/%e7%96%91%e9%81%ad%e6%94%bf%e6%b2%bb%e6%89%93%e5%a3%93-%e9%98%ae%e6%b0%91%e5%ae%89%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b%e4%bc%8a%e9%a4%a8%e9%ba%a5%e8%8a%b1%e8%87%a3%e5%a0%b4%e9%a4%a8%e9%96%8b%e9%a8%b7%e8%a2%ab%e6%8b%92|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|work=明報OL網|publisher=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706213957/https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191024/1571910966096/%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93-%E9%98%AE%E6%B0%91%E5%AE%89%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BC%8A%E9%A4%A8%E9%BA%A5%E8%8A%B1%E8%87%A3%E5%A0%B4%E9%A4%A8%E9%96%8B%E9%A8%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=阮民安開騷再遭審查被拒|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200111/MA5HZYDL3QNOVLOBBLGGITOIF4/|accessdate=2020-07-06|work=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707031751/https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200111/MA5HZYDL3QNOVLOBBLGGITOIF4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年年底，阮民安稱有一名「紅遍亞洲的天皇巨星」邀請其太太到酒店開房進行親密行為<ref>{{Cite web|title=阮民安爆老婆被亞洲巨星約上酒店|url=https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/focus/local/20191231-177883|accessdate=2020-01-11|date=2019-12-31|work=明周娛樂|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231064717/https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/focus/local/20191231-177883|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他本來表示不欲再說，後來又再度主動提起，並以「林先生」稱呼對方。同時，其妻被傳媒踢爆，在電話通訊中與大量男藝人有頻繁訊息交流，引起網民熱議<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/415808/阮民安fb爆老婆曾被天皇巨星約上酒店房-事主紅遍全亞洲|title=存档副本|accessdate=2020-09-21|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706223301/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/415808/%E9%98%AE%E6%B0%91%E5%AE%89fb%E7%88%86%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%87%E5%B7%A8%E6%98%9F%E7%B4%84%E4%B8%8A%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%88%BF-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%B4%85%E9%81%8D%E5%85%A8%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

